cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.HC, cs.MM, cs.CL 

The paper discusses visual search and recommendation services, which are related to computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The interactive user interfaces mentioned in the paper suggest a focus on human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The use of object detection also suggests a connection to multimedia (cs.MM) and natural language processing (cs.CL) for text-based image search.
